By way of derogation from Article 2(2) of Regulation (EC) No 581/2004, the tendering periods for the months October to December 2007 shall be the following:
(a) for October 2007 the tendering period shall begin on 9 and end on 16 October;
(b) for November 2007 the tendering period shall begin on 6 and end on 13 November;
(c) for December 2007 the tendering period shall begin on 4 and end on 11 December.
If the starting date is a public holiday, the period shall begin on the following working day. If the end date is a public holiday, it shall end on the previous working day.
Tendering periods shall start and end at 13:00 (Brussels time).

